e和false positive是算作各50%吗", "timestamp": 1629731955, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2342708, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": 2342660, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: dz 比较懒，不想写假阳性率和假阴性率，就笼统地都称为准确率了，如果一定要说定义就是”对于随机个体一次测试给出结果与实际情况相同的概率“", "timestamp": 1629732168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2342802, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "(1*95)/(1*95+999*5) 约等于100/5000", "timestamp": 1629732973, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2342980, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没仔细算，选了个最少的", "timestamp": 1629734471, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2343096, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "准确率这么定义也不行，需要给出对阳性样本和阴性样本的准确率", "timestamp": 1629735345, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2343101, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果定义好了很好算 贝叶斯公式即可\nG为感染\n～G为没有感染\nP（G）=0.1%\nY为检测阳性\n～Y为阴性\nP（G|Y）=P（Y|G）P（G）/P（Y）=P（Y|G）P（G）/（P（Y|G）P（G）+P（Y|～G）P（～G））", "timestamp": 1629735380, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2343126, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "老贝叶斯了", "timestamp": 1629735677, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2343811, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 448349, "reply_to": 2343096, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 抱歉的确是 dz 迷糊了，按 dz 那个定义答案就是 95% 了，确实要说成假阳率和假阴率（概统白学了）", "timestamp": 1629765100, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 448349, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "#每晚问题\n已知：T 市新冠感染率约为 0.1%，核酸检测准确率 95%。\n现在 T 市随机抽取一位市民 A 进行核酸检测，结果为阳性，则 A 患新冠的概率最接近", "timestamp": 1629731405, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629765098, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"2%": 71, "10%": 14, "50%": 7, "95%": 30}, "vote_options": ["2%", "10%", "50%", "95%"]}}}